unittitle_ssm: Photographic portraits of Danny Kaye and Sylvia Fine Kaye
abstract_ssm: The Photographic portraits of Danny Kaye and Sylvia Fine is comprised of two modern 8" x 10" black-and-white photographic prints of Danny Kaye (at age 7 or 8) and Sylvia Fine (at age 3). In the portraits, Danny is shown outdoors sitting in a toy car, while Sylvia is shown outdoors sitting on a large rock. The photographic prints were reproduced from photographs taken circa 1916 to 1920.
